<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Reset your PartnerScope password</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; background: #f6f7f9; margin: 0; padding: 24px; color: #1a2233; }
      .card { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; overflow: hidden; }
      .hdr { padding: 20px 28px; background: #0f1a2b; color: #fff; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .4px; font-size: 15px; }
      .body { padding: 24px 28px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; }
      .cta { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background: #0f1a2b; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
      .muted { color: #6a7280; font-size: 13px; }
      .link { word-break: break-all; color: #4f7cff; font-size: 13px; }
      .row { margin: 14px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="hdr">PARTNERSCOPE &middot; Password reset</div>
      <div class="body">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for <strong>{{email}}</strong>.</p>

        <div class="row">
          <a class="cta" href="{{resetUrl}}">Reset password</a>
        </div>

        <p class="muted">This link expires in {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes and can only be used once.</p>

        <p class="muted">If the button above does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
        <p class="link">{{resetUrl}}</p>

        <p class="muted">
          If you did not request a password reset you can ignore this email &mdash;
          your password will remain unchanged.
        </p>

        <p>&mdash; PartnerScope</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
